title: Sunny Upper Studio-parking, A/C, above Loring Pk, Sculpture Garden
posting_body: ['Updated and sunny upper-floor studio featuring BIG WINDOWS, GREAT DAYLIGHT, air-conditioner and off-street parking.', 'Well-maintained building above Loring Park, near Sculpture Garden.', 'Features:', 'Large triple window provides great daylight; completely freshened apartment has new wood-like laminate flooring and updated kitchen.', 'Also has a large ceiling fan, wall air-conditioner and window mini-blinds.', 'Located on hill above Loring Park, the building has updated common areas and coin laundry.', '(Photos show typical studio in the building.)', 'CONVENIENT location: Walk/bike to downtown, St. Thomas and MCTC.', 'Just two blocks to Loring Park, three blocks to Walker Art Center/Sculpture Garden.', 'Only one mile to Lake of the Isles and to Hennepin/Lake intersection.', 'Quiet neighborhood, yet quick access to 94, 35W and 394.', 'Terms: One-person maximum in studio.', 'Rent includes one off-street parking space, heat, water, sewer and trash.', 'Resident pays monthly electricity.', "Damage deposit equal to one month's rent due at lease signing.", "Full first month's rent due when you move in.", 'Application fee: $30/adult.', 'One cat o.k. with payment of pet rent of $15 per month.', 'Sorry, dogs are not allowed.', 'When you reply by email, please indicate: 1. ideal move-in date;', '2. number of people; 3.', 'whether you smoke; 4. any animals or pets; 5.', 'your phone number and email.']
